nclinuxsetup
============

Just a bunch of scripts I'm putting together to make my life easier when it comes to setting up the ideal Linux box.

Usage
-----

Start the ball rolling by copy/pasting this into a terminal window:

wget -O - https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nathanchere/nclinuxsetup/master/bootstrap.sh >> bootstrap.sh && sudo chmod +777 bootstrap.sh && ./bootstrap.sh



sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install git git-core
